# Hospital Management System — Frontend Testing Plan

> **Scope**: `web/` directory (Next.js 16 + React 19 + Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui)
> **Goal**: Full frontend coverage across unit, component, E2E, visual, accessibility, responsive, and performance layers.

---

## 1. Current State Assessment

### What Exists Today

| Layer | File | Tests | Tag | Coverage |
|-------|------|-------|-----|----------|
| **Unit (pure logic)** | `api-client.spec.ts` | 2 | — | `apiRequest` auth header injection |
| **Unit (pure logic)** | `rbac.spec.ts` | 4 | — | `getRouteDecision`, `filterNavigationLinks`, `persistSession` |
| **E2E Smoke** | `ui-smoke.spec.ts` | 67 | `@ui` | All 56 routes: HTTP status, `<main>` visible, no overlay, no console errors |
| **E2E Smoke** | `route-audit.spec.ts` | 2 | `@ui` | Route inventory sync between App Router, route metadata, and shell nav |
| **E2E Smoke** | `workflows.spec.ts` | 3 | `@ui` | Booking validation, portal overview links, staff/admin headings |
| **E2E Integrated** | `auth-integrated.spec.ts` | 7 | `@integrated` | Staff login/invalid, patient login/claim, logout, nurse queue check-in, RBAC redirect |
| **E2E Data-driven** | `staff-queue.spec.ts` | 4 | `@ui` | Queue board unauthorized, render+check-in, call/assign/start/complete, hide terminal |
| **E2E Data-driven** | `operations-api.spec.ts` | 3 | `@ui` | Inventory full render, monitoring+audit-logs, patient portal overview |
| **Responsive** | `responsive.spec.ts` | 24 | `@ui` | 8 routes × 3 viewports: stable layout, no overflow |
| **Visual** | `visual.spec.ts` | 8 | `@visual` | 8 routes: full-page screenshot baselines |

**Total existing: ~124 test cases** (many auto-generated from route lists)

### Infrastructure Available

- [x] Playwright 1.59 configured (chromium only)
- [x] `@axe-core/playwright` installed (accessibility)
- [x] Page Object Models: `LoginPage`, `BookingPage`
- [x] Helpers: `a11y`, `backend`, `console`, `layout`, `personas`, `routes`
- [x] Test tags: `@ui`, `@integrated`, `@visual`
- [x] JSON + HTML reporters
- [ ] ❌ No unit test runner (no Vitest/Jest)
- [ ] ❌ No `@testing-library/react`
- [ ] ❌ No component-level tests

---

## 2. Testing Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Layer 1 — Unit (Vitest)"
        U1[api-client.ts]
        U2[rbac.ts]
        U3[staff-queue.ts]
        U4[operations-api.ts]
        U5[clinical-api.ts]
        U6[use-stored-role.ts]
    end

    subgraph "Layer 2 — E2E Smoke (Playwright @ui)"
        S1[Route health]
        S2[Route inventory sync]
        S3[Responsive layouts]
        S4[Accessibility]
    end

    subgraph "Layer 3 — E2E Integrated (Playwright @integrated)"
        I1[Auth flows]
        I2[RBAC enforcement]
        I3[Booking end-to-end]
        I4[Queue workflow]
    end

    subgraph "Layer 4 — E2E Data-driven (Playwright @ui)"
        D1[Staff clinical pages]
        D2[Admin operations pages]
        D3[Patient portal pages]
        D4[Finance/billing pages]
    end

    subgraph "Layer 5 — Specialized"
        V1["Visual regression (@visual)"]
        P1["Performance (Lighthouse)"]
        SEC1["Security (CSP, headers)"]
    end

    U1 --> S1
    S1 --> I1
    I1 --> D1
    D1 --> V1
```

