## 3. Gap Analysis & New Tests Required

### 3.1 Unit Tests (NEW — requires Vitest setup)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> No unit test framework exists. Must add Vitest + `@testing-library/react` + `jsdom`.

#### 3.1.1 `lib/api-client.ts` — 12 new tests

| # | Test Case | Priority |
|---|-----------|----------|
| 1 | `apiRequest` — GET request builds correct URL | P1 |
| 2 | `apiRequest` — POST sends JSON body + Content-Type header | P1 |
| 3 | `apiRequest` — attaches patient bearer token for `authScope: "patient"` | P1 |
| 4 | `apiRequest` — throws `ApiClientError` on 4xx with error envelope | P1 |
| 5 | `apiRequest` — throws `ApiClientError` on 5xx with fallback message | P1 |
| 6 | `apiRequest` — handles empty response body gracefully | P2 |
| 7 | `getApiBaseUrl` — returns env variable when set | P2 |
| 8 | `getApiBaseUrl` — falls back to `localhost:8080` | P2 |
| 9 | `persistSession` — stores token, expiry, and role in sessionStorage | P1 |
| 10 | `persistSession` — is no-op when accessToken is missing | P2 |
| 11 | `clearSessions` — removes all 6 session keys | P1 |
| 12 | `getStoredRole` — returns null in SSR (no window) | P2 |

#### 3.1.2 `lib/rbac.ts` — 18 new tests

| # | Test Case | Priority |
|---|-----------|----------|
| 1 | `getRouteDecision` — public routes always allowed (home, departments, doctors, news) | P1 |
| 2 | `getRouteDecision` — `/staff/login` and `/portal/login` bypass auth | P1 |
| 3 | `getRouteDecision` — `/portal/claim` bypasses auth | P1 |
| 4 | `getRouteDecision` — DOCTOR can access `/staff/medical-records/*` | P1 |
| 5 | `getRouteDecision` — NURSE cannot access `/staff/medical-records/*` | P1 |
| 6 | `getRouteDecision` — PHARMACIST can access `/staff/inventory` | P1 |
| 7 | `getRouteDecision` — RECEPTIONIST cannot access `/staff/inventory` | P1 |
| 8 | `getRouteDecision` — ACCOUNTANT can access `/admin/audit-logs` | P1 |
| 9 | `getRouteDecision` — ACCOUNTANT cannot access `/admin/users` | P1 |
| 10 | `getRouteDecision` — DOCTOR can access `/staff/schedule` | P1 |
| 11 | `getRouteDecision` — all staff roles can access `/staff/dashboard` | P1 |
| 12 | `getRouteDecision` — all staff roles can access `/staff/support` | P2 |
| 13 | `getRouteDecision` — PATIENT cannot access any `/staff/*` route | P1 |
| 14 | `getRouteDecision` — trailing slash normalization | P2 |
| 15 | `toAppRole` — maps valid string to AppRole | P2 |
| 16 | `toAppRole` — returns null for invalid string | P2 |
| 17 | `toAppRole` — returns null for null/undefined | P2 |
| 18 | `filterNavigationLinks` — returns empty for null role | P2 |

#### 3.1.3 `lib/staff-queue.ts` — 10 new tests

| # | Test Case | Priority |
|---|-----------|----------|
| 1 | Fetch today's queue — calls correct endpoint with auth | P1 |
| 2 | Check-in — sends POST with ISO timestamp | P1 |
| 3 | Call patient — sends POST to `/queue/{id}/call` | P1 |
| 4 | Assign room — sends room name in body | P1 |
| 5 | Start consultation — POST to correct endpoint | P1 |
| 6 | Complete visit — POST to correct endpoint | P1 |
| 7 | Error handling — throws on non-2xx | P2 |
| 8 | Empty queue — handles empty data array | P2 |
| 9 | Queue filtering — separates waiting/ready/in-progress | P2 |
| 10 | Status badge derivation — maps statuses correctly | P3 |

#### 3.1.4 `lib/operations-api.ts` — 8 new tests

| # | Test Case | Priority |
|---|-----------|----------|
| 1 | Fetch inventory items — correct URL and auth scope | P1 |
| 2 | Fetch inventory lots — correct URL | P1 |
| 3 | Fetch inventory movements — correct URL | P2 |
| 4 | Fetch inventory alerts — correct URL | P2 |
| 5 | Fetch monitoring snapshot — admin auth | P1 |
| 6 | Fetch audit logs — supports pagination params | P2 |
| 7 | Error mapping — wraps API errors in typed error | P2 |
| 8 | Null/empty data — returns sensible defaults | P3 |

#### 3.1.5 `lib/clinical-api.ts` — 8 new tests

| # | Test Case | Priority |
|---|-----------|----------|
| 1 | Fetch patient record — correct endpoint | P1 |
| 2 | Save medical record — POST with body | P1 |
| 3 | Fetch lab results — staff vs. patient scope | P1 |
| 4 | Fetch prescriptions — correct auth | P2 |
| 5 | Fetch vital signs — correct auth | P2 |
| 6 | Create prescription — POST body validation | P2 |
| 7 | Patient portal overview — patient auth | P1 |
| 8 | Patient messages — patient auth | P2 |

#### 3.1.6 `lib/use-stored-role.ts` — 4 new tests

| # | Test Case | Priority |
|---|-----------|----------|
| 1 | Returns role from sessionStorage for staff scope | P1 |
| 2 | Returns role from sessionStorage for patient scope | P1 |
| 3 | Returns null when no role stored | P2 |
| 4 | Returns null in SSR environment | P2 |

