| 5 | Unauthenticated user navigating to `/staff/dashboard` → `/staff/login` | P1 |
| 6 | Unauthenticated user navigating to `/portal/overview` → `/portal/login` | P1 |
| 7 | PATIENT accessing `/staff/*` → forbidden | P1 |
| 8 | Route guard renders forbidden page with "Access denied" heading | P2 |

