## 6. Test Execution Matrix

| Command | What Runs | When |
|---------|-----------|------|
| `npm run test:unit` | Vitest unit tests | Pre-commit, CI |
| `npm run test:unit:coverage` | Unit tests + coverage report | CI, PR gate |
| `npm run test:e2e:ui` | Playwright `@ui` (smoke + data-driven) | CI, PR gate |
| `npm run test:e2e:integrated` | Playwright `@integrated` (needs backend) | Staging, pre-release |
| `npm run test:e2e:visual` | Playwright `@visual` (screenshot baselines) | PR gate |
| `npm run test:e2e:ci` | Critical subset for fast CI | Every push |
| Full suite | All layers | Nightly / release |

