## 9. Success Criteria

- [ ] **Unit test coverage ≥ 80%** on `src/lib/` modules
- [ ] **Zero critical/serious a11y violations** on all routes
- [ ] **All 56 routes render** without console errors or Next.js error overlays
- [ ] **RBAC enforcement verified** for all 7 roles × protected route categories
- [ ] **Every data-driven page** has at least one mocked test verifying its primary data render
- [ ] **Visual baselines exist** for at least 15 key screens
- [ ] **CI pipeline** runs unit + `@ui` + `@visual` on every PR in < 5 minutes
- [ ] **Integrated tests** pass against staging backend before every release
